last_episode_to_air.name: Though Unusual and Peculiar
last_episode_to_air.overview: Young-woo receives evidence that could make or break her case, while Min-woo changes his plans — and Jun-ho follows his heart.

name: Extraordinary Attorney Woo
overview: Brilliant attorney Woo Young-woo tackles challenges in the courtroom and beyond as a newbie at a top law firm and a woman on the autism spectrum.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Brilliant attorney Woo Young-woo tackles challenges in the courtroom and beyond as a newbie at a top law firm and a woman on the autism spectrum.

tagline: My name is Woo Young-woo, whether it is read straight or flipped. Kayak, deed, rotator, noon, racecar, Woo Young-woo.

episodes.name: Extraordinary Attorney Woo
episodes.overview: On her first day at a new job, Woo Young-woo meets an ally, a skeptic and an old acquaintance. She takes on an assault case involving an elderly couple.

episodes.name: The Wedding Dress That Slipped Off
episodes.overview: The father of a bride sues a hotel for a wedding that ended in a humiliating disaster. Lee Jun-ho asks Young-woo to share her whale facts over lunch.

episodes.name: "This is Pengsoo"
episodes.overview: A Tragedy surrounding two brothers forces a family to face diffcult truth.Young-Woo attempts to bridge a communication gap with a client.

episodes.name: The Strife of the Three Brothers
episodes.overview: Dong Geu-ra-mi seeks legal advice from Young-woo when her father unknowingly agrees to take on a massive debt. Kwon Min-woo broods in resentment.

episodes.name: Wild Card VS Tactician
episodes.overview: A copyright battle between two ATM companies stokes a rivalry between Young-woo and Min-woo. Geu-ra-mi teaches Young-woo how to spot a liar.

episodes.name: If I Were a Whale...
episodes.overview: Young-woo joins Choi Su-yeon in her mission to reunite a mother with her daughter. They explore every avenue to reduce a four-year sentence.

episodes.name: A Tale About Sodeok-dong I
episodes.overview: Residents of a small town file a class-action lawsuit to stop the construction of a highway. Hanbada Law Firm goes up against their biggest competitor.

episodes.name: A Tale About Sodeok-dong II
episodes.overview: Taesan Law Firm keeps a step ahead of Hanbada Law Firm as conditions lean in their favor. Tae Su-mi makes an offer to Young-woo.

episodes.name: The Pied Piper
episodes.overview: A self-proclaimed leader of the children’s liberation movement gets arrested for kidnapping. Young-woo tries to win Jun-ho’s affection.

episodes.name: Holding Hands Can Wait
episodes.overview: A man faces jail time for taking advantage of a woman with a disability. Jun-ho’s peers frown on his relationship. Min-woo pries into Young-woo's life.

episodes.name: Mr. Salt, Ms. Pepper and Attorney Soy Sauce
episodes.overview: Young-woo lands in a tricky legal position after a married couple seeks counsel to help settle a dispute involving a massive lottery win.

guest_stars.character: Jung Kang Hee [Il Soo's friend / Lottery winner]
guest_stars.name: Jung Kang-hee

episodes.name: Yangtze River Dolphin
episodes.overview: Young-woo encounters Hanbada’s dark side while working on a wrongful termination lawsuit. Jung Myeong-seok fears he has a target on his back.

episodes.name: The Blue Night of Jeju I
episodes.overview: A temple on Jeju Island goes to court for charging admission to the public, Young-woo meets Jun-ho’s family, and Myeong-seok reflects on his life.

guest_stars.character: Lee Seung Hui [Jun Ho's older sister]
guest_stars.name: Chae Song-hwa

episodes.name: The Blue Night of Jeju II
episodes.overview: The Hanbada lawyers look for the owner of Myeong-seok’s favorite noodle shop. Young-woo faces obstacles at the trial and in her relationship with Jun-ho.

episodes.name: Saying and Doing Things Not Asked
episodes.overview: When Young-woo clashes with her new supervisor during a case for a large online retailer, Myeong-seok advises her to lie low and lean on her peers.

episodes.name: Though Unusual and Peculiar
episodes.overview: Young-woo receives evidence that could make or break her case, while Min-woo changes his plans — and Jun-ho follows his heart.
